Tutorials / Content Management

Overview of the Content Manager

Your Content Manager holds all of your recordings, screenshots and videos. Find out what it does and how you can maximize it to work for you and your content. Try out our free video hosting solution today!

Your Content Manager holds all of your recordings, screenshots and videos. It is cross platform and serves as a secure storage to backup all of your content, edits and videos.

You can easily search video and content within our Content Manager and get sharable link to your content.  Thumbnail can also be customized here also and you can create new folders and organize all of your materials for intuitive sorting.
